apply following patches to the source tree
------------------------------------------
copy all filename.patch files to the inkscape base directory and
"patch -p0 -f < filename.patch" for each file

01_win32_printing.patch
02_win32_print_dialog_parent_window.patch
03_vista_turn_off_dashes.patch
04_win32_remove_dialogs_on_top_preference.patch
05_save_as_xaml.patch
06_environment_and_path_to_python.patch
07_glib_spawn_workaround.patch
08_handle_whitespaces_in_pathnames.patch
09_fix_crash_with_tweak_tool_on_3d_boxes.patch

after compile copy following dll into inkscape directory
--------------------------------------------------------
libcairo-2.dll
libpixman-1.dll
libpng12.dll
